tspan.tspan: 1. Multiselect - dataset keywords:
keywords can be dataset names, disease
name and primary tissues; Datasets
contains these keywords will show in the
following data.
2. Multiselect - datasets:
The datasets contain the keywords will show
in the table with dataset name, disease type
and primary sites. Table will be display 10
datasets per page. Click on the checkbox
before each row to select the datasets for
analysis
2.1 Datatset filtering
Sometimes few keywords will yield many
datasets. For further filtering, add the filtering
keywords in the top row of the table and press
enter.
2.2 Selected Datatset
Selected datasets will be displayed here.
Max 5 datasets are supported for single
gene, gene ratio, and gene set analyses;
Max 1 dataset is supported for other
analyses.
3 Datatset Tumor Type
Datasets are furthur categorized
into Primary, Recurrent, and
Metastatic tumors. Select the
one that you are interested in.
